himself to avoid jail time.

06:03.730 --> 06:04.965
Open and shut.

06:05.032 --> 06:08.401
Open and shut. Hmm.

06:08.468 --> 06:09.803
Hey, are you hungry?

06:09.870 --> 06:11.171
Yeah.

06:11.238 --> 06:13.606
Let's get lunch.

06:13.673 --> 06:15.475
Hmm. Excuse me.

06:28.822 --> 06:31.324
