in. I'll just take my lunch.

06:45.338 --> 06:49.142
Great, here come these
two fucking assholes.

06:49.209 --> 06:50.844
Oh, I heard you guys
closed a case before lunch.

06:50.911 --> 06:52.079
Congratulations.

06:52.145 --> 06:53.546
