06:53.613 --> 06:55.916
Religious nut. Slit
his throat this morning.

06:55.983 --> 06:57.184
DRAGOS: See?

06:57.250 --> 06:59.519
That's how it's done, fuck-o.

06:59.586 --> 07:03.056
The report said he has a stash
of English-language Bibles.

07:03.123 --> 07:04.992
Nothing about that
seemed strange to you?

07:05.058 --> 07:07.627
So the guy's into creepy Christian shit.

07:07.694 --> 07:09.096
What's strange about that, huh?

07:09.162 --> 07:11.164
Well, in case you
forgot, Nikita was killed

07:11.231 --> 07:13.833
