international smuggling ring.

07:13.901 --> 07:16.369
STAN: The guy was acting alone, fellas.

07:16.436 --> 07:17.670
Go bark up another tree.

07:17.737 --> 07:20.473
DRAGOS: Yeah, some loner
sneaking in Bibles eventually

07:20.540 --> 07:22.943
