on the same shit he's pushing.

07:23.010 --> 07:24.344
Happens all the time.

07:24.411 --> 07:26.279
Yeah, yeah, no, I'm sure you're right.

07:26.346 --> 07:28.581
- Of course I'm right.
- Yeah.

07:28.648 --> 07:29.382
- (SHOUTS)
- Hey!

07:29.449 --> 07:30.753
Hey!

07:30.754 --> 07:31.881
- Stop, please!
- You call yourself a detective,

07:31.885 --> 07:33.353
you ginger piece of shit?

07:33.420 --> 07:35.115
- Let go! Let go!
- We questioned his landlady.

07:35.116 --> 07:36.990
He had no friends, kept to
himself, just him and his religion.

07:37.057 --> 07:38.625
The case is closed!

07:38.691 --> 07:40.327
End of story!

07:40.393 --> 07:42.262
- Stop, please!
- Give us the file.

07:42.329 --> 07:43.863
GREGOR: You like jerking
off with your left hand?

07:43.931 --> 07:45.332
No! Give him the fucking file!

07:45.398 --> 07:47.667
(SCREAMS)

07:47.734 --> 07:49.669
- Aah, give him the file!
- Fucker.

07:49.736 --> 07:51.871
