08:14.161 --> 08:16.096
Good afternoon, gentlemen.

08:16.163 --> 08:18.431
I'm Detective Baciu and
this is Detective Anghel.

08:18.498 --> 08:20.433
We're looking for
information on Marku Miklos.

08:30.677 --> 08:33.246
Marku Miklos.

08:33.313 --> 08:35.347
Yes.

08:35.414 --> 08:38.986
I was saddened to hear of his passing.

08:39.052 --> 08:41.154
Still, I wasn't surprised.

08:42.188 --> 08:45.292
No? And why's that?

08:45.358 --> 08:47.460
He was a strange young man.

08:47.527 --> 08:48.728
