10:33.066 --> 10:35.001
Well, that guy's a fucking weirdo.

10:35.068 --> 10:37.204
Let's pull his file.

10:40.273 --> 10:42.209
JOSEPH: His name's Anton Streza.

10:42.275 --> 10:44.077
