for burglary and assault.

10:44.144 --> 10:45.712
Did six years in prison.

10:45.778 --> 10:48.415
Once he was released,
got a job at the bakery.

10:48.481 --> 10:52.319
Kept a low profile ever since.

10:52.385 --> 10:55.255
Gregor.

10:55.322 --> 10:57.624
Look who the arresting officer was.

11:01.961 --> 11:04.764
Detective Nikita Ionescu.

11:10.703 --> 11:13.840
