15:28.094 --> 15:31.230
We got your file, asshole.

15:31.297 --> 15:32.432
Oh...

15:33.900 --> 15:37.704
Gideon Bible, straight from the USA.

15:37.770 --> 15:40.373
GREGOR: Some heavy shit for a baker.

15:40.440 --> 15:42.875
Congratulations, pal,
you're under arrest.

15:51.451 --> 15:54.020
All right, bread boy, what are these?

15:57.857 --> 16:01.327
They're books.

16:01.394 --> 16:05.532
Books that hold the Word of God.

16:05.598 --> 16:07.900
We know what Bibles are, Streza.

16:07.967 --> 16:09.902
It's my favorite work of fiction.

16:09.969 --> 16:12.772
We found these same
Bibles on Marku Miklos.

16:12.839 --> 16:14.507
Where are you getting them?

16:16.643 --> 16:20.279
We prayed for them...

16:20.346 --> 16:22.682
and God answered our prayers.

16:22.749 --> 16:23.916
Hmm.

16:25.384 --> 16:28.588
