16:50.376 --> 16:52.979
How convenient.

16:53.045 --> 16:57.349
So, people smart enough to know
there's no such thing as God,

16:57.416 --> 16:59.385
we're the ones who should be worried.

16:59.452 --> 17:02.555
You cannot prove there is no God.

17:02.622 --> 17:05.124
That's because you
can't prove a negative.

17:05.191 --> 17:09.628
Absence of evidence is
not evidence of absence.

17:09.695 --> 17:12.665
All I know is God is good.

17:14.032 --> 17:14.967
Is he?

17:16.469 --> 17:19.839
Then explain war, rape.

17:23.510 --> 17:26.878
Explain death and suffering.

17:26.945 --> 17:29.482
Explain the horrors
man has had to endure

17:29.549 --> 17:31.383
since the beginning of time.

17:31.450 --> 17:34.020
God works in mysterious ways.

17:35.588 --> 17:38.891
And that's all I'm going to say.

17:41.027 --> 17:42.128
(SCOFFS)

17:44.196 --> 17:46.465
(DOOR OPENS)

17:56.308 --> 17:57.910
(DOOR CLOSES)

18:04.150 --> 18:05.818
That crazy fuck's not
gonna give us anything.

18:05.885 --> 18:07.754
How do you suppose someone
even gets wrapped up

18:07.820 --> 18:09.989
in all this bullshit?

18:13.259 --> 18:15.227
(JOSEPH SIGHS)

18:15.294 --> 18:16.863
The universe is complex.

18:16.929 --> 18:18.831
Religion offers simple-minded people

18:18.898 --> 18:20.867
easily digestible answers.

18:20.933 --> 18:22.935
