believe in fairy tales.

18:38.250 --> 18:40.186
Yeah, but don't forget,

18:40.252 --> 18:41.588
every fairy tale has a monster.

18:41.654 --> 18:43.790
(BUZZER SOUNDS)

18:45.357 --> 18:47.526
