signed by world leaders

19:20.259 --> 19:22.829
calling for his release.

19:26.098 --> 19:29.235
England, Canada, Australia, France...

19:29.301 --> 19:30.670
Wales?

19:30.737 --> 19:32.071
You gotta be fucking kidding me

19:32.138 --> 19:34.206
- with these bullshit countries.
- (GASPS)

19:34.273 --> 19:35.507
I'm just doing my job.

19:35.574 --> 19:37.944
And you've done it. Now you can go.

19:38.010 --> 19:41.147
This isn't over, Detectives.

19:42.782 --> 19:45.351
Great, now we got a ticking clock.

19:45.417 --> 19:47.119
They're going to apply
international pressure.

19:47.186 --> 19:50.189
How we gonna get this priest to talk?

19:50.256 --> 19:51.624
You know what, Joseph?

19:51.691 --> 19:53.292
You've been working too hard.

19:53.359 --> 19:54.661
Go home to your family.

19:54.727 --> 19:56.262
What are you planning?

19:57.664 --> 20:00.232
I'm gonna set a herring
to catch a whale.

20:00.299 --> 20:01.333
(CLICKS TONGUE)

20:06.472 --> 20:08.207
Good night.

20:08.274 --> 20:09.308
Good night, Roy.

20:09.375 --> 20:11.310
ROY: Good night, madam.

20:13.680 --> 20:16.282
JANE: Uh...

20:16.348 --> 20:18.350
What are you doing here?

20:21.120 --> 20:22.655
