20:46.178 --> 20:49.348
I missed you. (CHUCKLES)

20:49.415 --> 20:51.117
I missed you, my love.

20:51.183 --> 20:52.719
(SONYA CHUCKLES)

20:54.620 --> 20:56.288
SONYA: Ooh!

20:58.390 --> 21:00.159
Mmm.

21:00.226 --> 21:02.228
(CHUCKLES)

21:02.294 --> 21:05.031
This bean soup with ham hock is so good.

21:05.097 --> 21:06.933
I told you, it's the best in the city.

21:06.999 --> 21:09.501
Bean soup is a delicacy.

21:09.568 --> 21:11.838
When I go home, I'm really
going to miss the food

21:11.904 --> 21:13.239
