21:40.166 --> 21:42.668
But America is still the
greatest country in the world.

21:42.735 --> 21:44.636
Hmm.

21:44.703 --> 21:46.072
What? It's true.

21:46.138 --> 21:48.908
I mean, Romania has
some nice things, too.

21:48.975 --> 21:50.476
Like, the literacy rate is amazing.

21:52.311 --> 21:57.283
Everyone is so good-looking
and has such a youthful spirit.

21:57.349 --> 21:59.886
But...

21:59.952 --> 22:02.822
I miss my home.

22:02.889 --> 22:05.424
I miss my country.

22:05.491 --> 22:08.494
