22:25.744 --> 22:28.547
Because life is too short.

22:28.614 --> 22:32.018
(SOFT CHUCKLE)

22:32.084 --> 22:33.719
Hmm.

22:33.786 --> 22:35.121
You're trouble.

22:36.688 --> 22:37.857
Hmm?

22:37.924 --> 22:42.694
Unfortunately, I'm a good American girl

22:42.761 --> 22:47.366
and I don't sleep with
strange, Eastern European men

22:47.433 --> 22:49.501
