28:53.765 --> 28:56.668
(CAR HORNS HONKING)

28:56.735 --> 29:00.005
(BOTH LAUGHING)

29:00.071 --> 29:02.441
This is madness.

29:02.508 --> 29:04.810
This is madness. You trust her?

29:04.876 --> 29:07.813
No, but she trusts me.

29:07.879 --> 29:10.182
You slept with her?

29:10.249 --> 29:11.583
Yeah.

29:15.787 --> 29:19.157
Well, detectives, looks
like you're in luck.

29:21.793 --> 29:23.161
(CHUCKLES)

29:23.229 --> 29:26.398
JANE: Father Streza has
agreed to give you information

29:26.465 --> 29:30.068
in return for his immediate release.

29:30.135 --> 29:31.570
We're authorized to release him

29:31.637 --> 29:33.739
if he does, in fact, give us real info.

29:40.212 --> 29:41.813
Where are you getting your Bibles?

29:41.880 --> 29:45.217
They're the words of God,
and God is everywhere.

29:46.752 --> 29:48.119
I want answers.

29:48.186 --> 29:49.655
We all want answers.

29:49.721 --> 29:53.592
But until you accept Jesus
Christ as your savior,

29:53.659 --> 29:56.795
you're like a blind man
fumbling around in the dark.

29:56.862 --> 29:58.797
So shed some light for me, Father.

29:58.864 --> 30:02.468
Where were you and Marku
getting your Bibles?

30:02.534 --> 30:06.372
There's a man intent on helping
me spread the word of God.

30:07.439 --> 30:09.341
To you, he's a smuggler.

30:09.408 --> 30:11.777
To me, he's an angel,

30:11.843 --> 30:13.211
sent from heaven above.

30:13.279 --> 30:15.481
And does this angel have a name?

30:21.987 --> 30:25.324
He calls himself...

30:25.391 --> 30:27.559
James Brown.

30:33.399 --> 30:35.367
James Brown?

30:39.237 --> 30:40.572
Hmm.

30:41.840 --> 30:44.142
(SIGHS)

30:44.209 --> 30:45.511
How do we find him?

30:46.412 --> 30:48.914
You don't.

30:48.980 --> 30:51.283
He has people who are devoted to him.

30:51.350 --> 30:54.286
People like Marku
Miklos who keep him safe.

30:54.353 --> 30:58.557
