own throats than give him up.

30:58.624 --> 31:02.361
He is the rock on which
I will build my church.

31:02.428 --> 31:05.564
He's coming for you, detectives.

31:05.631 --> 31:07.299
He's coming for both of you.

31:07.366 --> 31:08.434
How the fuck do we find him?

31:08.500 --> 31:09.635
STREZA: I told you, you can't.

31:09.701 --> 31:11.370
He's a ghost. A holy ghost!

31:11.437 --> 31:13.839
Okay, that's all you get.

31:13.905 --> 31:16.074
Father Streza has been
more than forthcoming.

31:16.141 --> 31:17.843
This is bullshit.

31:17.909 --> 31:19.411
He gave us an alias.

31:19.478 --> 31:20.646
That's all he knows.

31:20.712 --> 31:22.013
And this interview is over.

31:22.080 --> 31:23.515
Like hell it is.

31:23.582 --> 31:26.284
Look, we had a deal,

31:26.352 --> 31:28.286
