lived up to his end.

31:28.354 --> 31:29.321
Understood?

31:29.388 --> 31:30.956
So, let me make this clear.

31:31.022 --> 31:35.494
Release him now or I will use
the full power of my office

31:35.561 --> 31:37.262
to make sure that the two of you

31:37.329 --> 31:40.198
end up building canals in Constanta.

31:40.265 --> 31:42.368
Got it?

31:42.434 --> 31:43.602
Good.

31:45.404 --> 31:47.673
You're free to go, Father.

31:47.739 --> 31:50.409
These men won't bother you anymore.

31:50.476 --> 31:52.811
May God bless you, comrades.

31:59.184 --> 32:01.687
Hey, Father.

32:02.888 --> 32:05.090
You know why Jesus
wasn't born in the West?

32:06.558 --> 32:08.794
